### Ordering API Test Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8003
@apiVersion = v1

### Get Recent Activities (Default - 10 items)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Activity?pageIndex=0&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Recent Activities with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Activity?pageIndex=0&pageSize=5&entityType=Product
Accept: application/json

### Get Recent Activities - Product activities only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Activity?pageIndex=0&pageSize=10&activityType=Product.Created
Accept: application/json

### Get Recent Activities - Order activities only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Activity?pageIndex=0&pageSize=10&activityType=Order.Created
Accept: application/json

### Get Recent Activities with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Activity?pageIndex=0&pageSize=10&from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

### Get Orders by UserName
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Order/testuser
Accept: application/json

### Create Order (for testing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "testuser",
  "totalPrice": 99.99,
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "emailAddress": "test@example.com",
  "addressLine": "123 Test St",
  "country": "USA",
  "state": "CA",
  "zipCode": "12345",
  "cardName": "Test User",
  "cardNumber": "1234567890123456",
  "expiration": "12/25",
  "cvv": "123",
  "paymentMethod": 1
}
